<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>W.A. Mozart</author>
<hymn_number>246</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zazakely entinay
 Mba hatao batisa izao ;
 Izy no atokanay
 Sy atolotray Anao.

[V2]
 Rano tsy mba mahasoa,
 Rano tsy mba mahadio :
 Ka tahionao izy izao,
 Jeso ô, be indrafo !

[V3]
 Ary ny Fanahinao
 Dia ataovy ao am-po
 Mba hitarika azy, sao
 Hisy loza izay hanjo.

[V4]
 Ry Jehovah be fitia !
 Ry Jesosy Tomponay !
 Ry Fanahy koa, avia
 Mba handray ny zanakay.</lyrics>
<title>Zazakely entinay mba hatao batisa FFPM246</title>
</song>